Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deletePipelineNetGroup(25.10)                    deletePipelineNetGroup(25.10)

Name
       deletePipelineNetGroup - Deletes pipeline net groups including the sub-
       groups created inside the net groups

Syntax
       deletePipelineNetGroup

       [-help]

       netGroupName

       Deletes  pipeline net groups including the subgroups created inside the
       net groups.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each deletePipelineNetGroup parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man deletePipelineNetGroup.

       <netGroupName>
              Specifies the name of the net group.

Example
              * The following command deletes a net group named `netGroup1':

                deletePipelineNetGroup netGroup1

Related Information
              * createPipelineNetGroup

              * modifyPipelineNetGroup

              * reportPipeline

